{"pageProps":{"problem":{"id":"t22-train-1","grade":"7","semester":"up","category":"整式的加减","title":"针对训练1：数轴化简绝对值","difficulty":4,"tags":["绝对值","数轴"],"content":"若 $-1 < a < 3$，化简 $|a + 1| - |a - 3|$ 的结果是 ______。","steps":[{"title":"分析绝对值内符号","content":"当 $-1 < a < 3$ 时：\n$a + 1 > 0$，所以 $|a + 1| = a + 1$\n$a - 3 < 0$，所以 $|a - 3| = -(a - 3) = 3 - a$","formula":""},{"title":"化简","content":"$|a + 1| - |a - 3| = (a + 1) - (3 - a) = a + 1 - 3 + a = 2a - 2$","formula":"\\text{答案：}2a - 2"}]},"id":"t22-train-1"},"__N_SSG":true}